    "description": "Play an orderly in a Madhouse. Care for your patients, influence their behavior, unlock new floors and manage growing challenges in <strong>Madhouse</strong>. <br><br>On your first day in Madhouse you get to know the basic mechanics of the game and the handling of the patients.<br><br>The basic mechanics which you need all the time include:<br><br>- Filfilling personal and general needs of the patients.<br>- Managing challenges.<br>- The different ways to gain resources.<br>- The crafting and placement of objects with a workbench.<br><br>In the course of the game the needs and the connected challenges become more difficult. You have to decide if you are a good orderly and act according to the rules or if you make yourself popular with the patients. Decide wisely because every decision may have  consequences in the future.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><strong>Design your character</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098650/extras/575eb2bc03e7575a5bea87298a5d4d94.avif?t=1583224948\" width=660 height=553 /></span><br>- No matter whether you are a man or a woman, whether you have short or long hair, whether you are big or small.<br>- Choose from a variety of clothing: shirts, pants, shoes.<br>- You don't like your look anymore? Just change at any time.<br><br><br><strong>Talk to your patients &amp; colleagues</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098650/extras/238ce4d6c797c05eed2365386da1e1b4.avif?t=1583224948\" width=660 height=648 /></span><br>- Your colleagues will give you important information about working as a nurse.<br>- Each patient has their own story and needs.<br><br><strong>Make tools &amp; medication yourself</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app